  "detailed_description": "Chronicle of Danae tells the story about Luchezar – the failed heir to the throne, who buried his father and was mired in the depths of a bloody war. Will Luchezar be able to reverse a series of failures and regain his Kingdom, or will he die on the battlefield? This is what the Chronicle will tell us.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immerse yourself in the world of medieval fantasy with a pleasant atmosphere and music.<br></li><li>Assemble a team of loyal followers to reclaim the throne.<br></li><li>Make decisions that affect the fate of the entire Kingdom.<br></li><li>Solve riddles and be smart on the way to the goal.<br></li><li>Be prepared to take responsibility for every step you take.<br></li><li>Feel like a keeper of history and wisdom of the whole realm.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Chronicle of Danae tells the story about Luchezar – the failed heir to the throne, who buried his father and was mired in the depths of a bloody war. Will Luchezar be able to reverse a series of failures and regain his Kingdom, or will he die on the battlefield? This is what the Chronicle will tell us.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immerse yourself in the world of medieval fantasy with a pleasant atmosphere and music.<br></li><li>Assemble a team of loyal followers to reclaim the throne.<br></li><li>Make decisions that affect the fate of the entire Kingdom.<br></li><li>Solve riddles and be smart on the way to the goal.<br></li><li>Be prepared to take responsibility for every step you take.<br></li><li>Feel like a keeper of history and wisdom of the whole realm.</li></ul>",
